sudo = superuser do
To add a user
sudo adduser lorna

To amend to a super user

$ sudo usermod-aG sudo lorna
-a appends the user to the...
-G groups

Switching to a certain user:
$ su - lorna

To exit from that user back to default
$ exit

Deleting a user

$ sudo userdel frodo

But wouldn't delete the directory 

Downgrades an account privilege from sudo to non sudo
$ sudo gpasswd -d username sudo
